    <Text id="2" huntingZoneId="0" prevId="0" villagerId="0">
        <Page social="0">Crafting for the War Effort&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Support the federation war effort by crafting armor for our soldiers!&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;We need more recruit's robes!</Page>
    </Text>
    <Text id="3" huntingZoneId="63" prevId="2" villagerId="1604">
        <Page social="0">Tailors are in short supply.&lt;BR&gt;&lt;BR&gt;Shapalyn in the Creation Workshop is taking steps to train new tailors. If you're interested, start there.</Page>
    </Text>
    <Text id="4" huntingZoneId="63" prevId="3" villagerId="1609">
        <Page social="0">I give you a pattern, you learn to sew. Deal?</Page>
    </Text>
